# User Schema

## User Models

The user system consists of several related models:

- [Local User](mdc:src/api/local-user/content-types/local-user/schema.json) - The main user model
  - Contains authentication data like Phone, Password
  - Connected to user info, addresses, wallet, etc.
  
- [Local User Info](mdc:src/api/local-user-info/content-types/local-user-info/schema.json) - User profile information
  - Contains FirstName, LastName, and other personal details
  
- [Local User Address](mdc:src/api/local-user-address/content-types/local-user-address/schema.json) - User shipping addresses
  - Contains address details for delivery and billing

- [Local User Role](mdc:src/api/local-user-role/content-types/local-user-role/schema.json) - User role assignments
  - Defines user permissions and access levels

## User Wallet

- [Local User Wallet](mdc:src/api/local-user-wallet/content-types/local-user-wallet/schema.json) - Digital wallet for users
  - Tracks user's account balance

- [Local User Wallet Transaction](mdc:src/api/local-user-wallet-transaction/content-types/local-user-wallet-transaction/schema.json) - Wallet transaction history
  - Records deposits, withdrawals, and other wallet transactions

## User Permissions

- [Local User Permission](mdc:src/api/local-user-permission/content-types/local-user-permission/schema.json) - Permission settings for users
  - Defines specific permissions for user actions and access

